  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为服务器端SDK选型设计一个完整的评估工作流。起点应该是明确定义评估标准，包括DID支持、凭证与证明能力、移动端集成度、密钥存储方案和授权许可这几个维度。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Define",
        "DID/credential/proof support",
        "mobile integration",
        "key storage",
        "licensing"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，起点是定义标准。那标准确定之后，下一步是直接进入候选SDK的功能评估，还是先做一个初步筛选？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Define",
        "Shortlist"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "需要先做一个Shortlist环节，把候选的SDK和开源库列出来。这里有个分支逻辑：如果某个候选支持Flutter等目标平台，就进入功能评估；如果缺乏平台支持，直接拒绝或推迟。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Shortlist",
        "Reject",
        "supports Flutter target platforms",
        "lacks platform support"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，Shortlist分出两条路径：支持平台的进入功能评估，不支持的走拒绝分支。那功能评估具体覆盖哪些能力？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Features",
        "Shortlist",
        "Reject"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "功能评估要覆盖签名、验证、DID解析和VC解析这四个核心能力。通过之后进入本地基准测试环节，需要记录详细的性能数据。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Features",
        "Bench",
        "signing",
        "verification",
        "DID resolution",
        "VC parsing",
        "record results"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加Features到Bench的流程。那基准测试的结果如何影响后续决策？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Bench",
        "Select"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Bench之后也有分支：如果满足PoC的资源和时间约束，就选定该候选进入PoC集成；如果不满足约束，需要退回Shortlist重新考虑其他候选。另外，拒绝的候选也可以回到Shortlist池子，方便后续复审。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Bench",
        "Select",
        "Reject",
        "Shortlist",
        "meets PoC constraints",
